mple an activated risk status (GS), the risk status (GS) being activated when an acute indication (AI) is present. After the acute indication (AI) has ended, the risk status (GS) remains activated until a safety indication (SI) is present, so that, due to the internal combustion engine remaining switched on, maneuverability of the motor vehicle is maintained at least until the safety indication (SI) is recognized</p></abstract></us-patent-application>